title: This is someone elses from Myfonts but I like it!
content:
This font had no replies on the what the font board I didn't post it but it's really an attractive font. Does anyone know what it is?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20140804191314im_/http:/typophile.com/files/621e53706520f1ad3154644ee8c26644_5540.172277.jpg)
author: Pattie P

comments.content:
It is / was [an unfinished typeface by Romesh Naik](http://web.archive.org/web/20140804191314/http:/www.flickr.com/photos/n1ke/143287167/in/set-72057594050445919/).  
_(I just knew I have seen this one before. Love it, as well.)_

very nice... something you see on the side of an old train.
